    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《惊悚故事 3：英格莉忏悔录》是一部引人深思的黑暗童话。讲述了任性娇纵的小女孩英格莉，在去给外婆送面包的路上，为了不弄脏鞋子，竟然想踩在面包上，却因此跌入了黑暗森林的地下世界。这里充斥着可怖的生物，落入这地狱中的英格莉，不仅需要破解一个个谜题隐喻，还需要在内心的善恶之间作出抉择，是不折手段逃出生天，还是直面内心获得救赎？玩家将和她一起决定。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">故事灵感来自安徒生、格林兄弟等作家故事，配上诡秘阴森的音乐以及怪诞恐怖的配音，让你身临黑暗童话的中心，阅读不一样的另类童话。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761780/extras/95b1951c18d4d8985afa2cfdff50c4e0.avif?t=1772265721\" width=616 height=74 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761780/extras/7bb45514fc5ef9af8949bc3d5162a280.poster.avif?t=1772265721\" width=616 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761780/extras/7bb45514fc5ef9af8949bc3d5162a280.webm?t=1772265721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761780/extras/7bb45514fc5ef9af8949bc3d5162a280.mp4?t=1772265721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">和地狱的恐怖生物斗智斗勇，解谜融入了各种机关陷阱，同时又不止一条通关的方法。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761780/extras/80269c512331bceaff233de6f86f2a8f.avif?t=1772265721\" width=616 height=74 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761780/extras/6fb2db54bd7d471bc3978373150bc67b.poster.avif?t=1772265721\" width=616 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761780/extras/6fb2db54bd7d471bc3978373150bc67b.webm?t=1772265721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761780/extras/6fb2db54bd7d471bc3978373150bc67b.mp4?t=1772265721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">一念之差，一步之遥，天堂地狱，在劫难逃。面对地狱的谜题与原住民，你可以选择让他们付出代价，也可以选择施以怜悯，但不管怎样，善恶的天平会记住你的选择。在最终审判面前，你将获得救赎，还是堕落？ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761780/extras/2b9c2730cd48535c4111256a830249e3.poster.avif?t=1772265721\" width=616 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761780/extras/2b9c2730cd48535c4111256a830249e3.webm?t=1772265721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761780/extras/2b9c2730cd48535c4111256a830249e3.mp4?t=1772265721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
